( \\frac{77204}{2307.623} \\approx 33.4 \\)\n\n### 错误传播路径\n\n1. **CurrencyService - GetSupportedCurrencies**:\n   - 异常中出现 \"connection refused\" 信息，显示较高发生频次，关联的调用链均显示连接问题。\n   - 可能导致 downstream 的 `CheckOutService` 和其他服务出现失败。\n\n### 错误状态\n\n1. **Frontend 和 Checkout Service 出现多个\"HTTP 500\"状态码**，通常是内部错误或无法处理的请求。\n2. **CurrencyService 故障**可能导致对价格转换的失败，进一步引发 `CheckoutService` 中订单处理的失败。\n\n### 关键发现提取\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->currencyservice\",\n    \"cartservice->checkoutservice\",\n    \"frontend->currencyservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"connection refused errors and transport errors during high anomaly occurrences\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"massive increase in response time for GetCart and EmptyCart operations\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n通过这些异常数据的分析，`CurrencyService` 和 `CartService` 是明显的瓶颈和故障源，有待进一步排查以确定具体问题。建议深入核实 network settings 和对相关服务进行性能分析，以定位根因和制定解决方案。", "metric_analysis_findings": "在分析过程中，我们发现了一些显著的异常调用链和资源变化。以下是具体的分析结果：\n\n### 关键异常指标\n- 从 `anomaly_metrics` 中提取到的异常指标包括：\n  - `pod_processes`\n  - `node_memory_usage_rate`\n  - `rrt_max`\n  - `rrt`\n  - `pod_cpu_usage`\n  - `request`\n  - `response`\n\n### 异常分析 (Hypotheses)\n1. **Currencyservice-1 Pod 异常**\n   - **指标名**: `pod_processes`\n   - **原因**: `currencyservice-1` Pod 的 `pod_processes` 在异常期间从 1 增加到 2，表明了某种形式的 Pod 生命周期异常。\n   - **证据**: \"pod_processes from 1.0 to 2.0 (p99 change ratio 0.6667)\"\n\n2. **Node 内存瓶颈**\n   - **节点**: `aiops-k8s-05`\n   - **指标名**: `node_memory_usage_rate`\n   - **原因**: Node 内存使用率显著增加，表明 Node 资源使用上升明显。\n   - **证据**: \"Normal median 29.68, fault median 42.25, change ratio 0.3493\"\n\n3. **Currencyservice-1 性能问题**\n   - **服务名称**: `currencyservice`\n   - **指标名**: `rrt_max`\n   - **原因**: `currencyservice` 的 `rrt_max` 在异常期间增加，可能导致服务延迟增加。\n   - **证据**: \"Normal median 5225.5, fault median 3833.0, change ratio 0.3074\"\n\n4. **Currencyservice-0 性能问题**\n   - **服务名称**: `currencyservice`\n   - **指标名**: `rrt_max`\n   - **原因**: `currencyservice-0` 的 `rrt_max` 在异常期间增加，也表明服务性能问题。\n   - **证据**: \"Normal median 5452.0, fault median 27248.0, change ratio 1.3331\"\n\n### JSON 输出格式\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"pod_processes\",\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"request\",\n    \"response\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"currencyservice-1 Pod processes changed during anomaly indicating lifecycle issue.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes from 1.0 to 2.0 (p99 change ratio 0.6667)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-05\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory usage rate increased significantly indicating resource bottleneck.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal median 29.68, fault median 42.25, change ratio 0.3493\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"currencyservice-1 RRT Max increased indicating performance issue.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal median 5225.5, fault median 3833.0, change ratio 0.3074\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"currencyservice-0 RRT Max increased indicating performance issue.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal median 5452.0, fault median 27248.0, change ratio 1.3331\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
